{"tid":690383,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(二戰JJ)Post Scriptum - The Bloody Seventh","createTime":"2018-06-04T22:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T07:17:58.000Z","uid":59743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc37ae4ab8cee11fbfdd1722e584e85189dd8817","tid":690383,"uid":59743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T22:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://postscriptumgame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Halftrack_Branded_v011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fpostscriptumgame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2FHalftrack_Branded_v011.jpg&h=1416e17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說上星期睇完Battlefield 5 個trailer,見到女人士兵走黎走去,裝左機械手腳既士兵上2戰戰埸,戰機機師炒機轉身返落地,v2火箭射落黎近距離轟炸之後咩事都無.......忍唔住係度開返個post<br />\n<br />\n鐘意玩2戰game既你,黎緊就出一隻叫Post Scriptum - The Bloody Seventh 既遊戲<br />\n<br />\n故事係講2戰 美軍同英軍空降部隊(British Airborne Division, British XXX Corps)打德軍(Wehrmacht or the Waffen SS)<br />\n<br />\n呢隻game既特點和定位:<br />\n-50vs50,<br />\n-真實2戰模擬器,差唔多一槍死(類似red orchestra 2, Squad)<br />\n-要同小團隊有非常好既合作,一齊傾戰略,搶有利位置搶資訊,每個小團隊有唔同既2戰士兵職業(medic,machine gunner, masksman, anti-tank,rifleman,engineer,tank commander, tank crew, driver,gunner,hull gunner,etc) <br />\n-5張超大地圖 (&gt;140 KM)<br />\n-50種真實載具(雪曼,虎式,etc)<br />\n-40種真實槍械<br />\n-指揮官可以起營地(叫轟炸機)<br />\n-細緻坦克設計<br />\n-盟軍可以玩跳傘<br />\n<br />\n遊戲設計師係Squad MOD TEAM,由2016年3月開始設計<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既巴打自己上官網睇: <a href=\"http://postscriptumgame.com/the-game/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpostscriptumgame.com%2Fthe-game%2F&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBp54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=bedc0b22\" target=\"_blank\">http://postscriptumgame.com/the-game/</a><br />\n<br />\ntrailer: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yFKNSu_aI5I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyFKNSu_aI5I&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBp54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cf68db7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yFKNSu_aI5I</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;v=ClhAxd_XR-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D3%26v%3DClhAxd_XR-8&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBp54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=984d8b89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;v=ClhAxd_XR-8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://postscriptumgame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/C47_Branded_v011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fpostscriptumgame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2FC47_Branded_v011.jpg&h=e2150616&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0049775d044d24433761b7ab39e17f57b2c45928","tid":690383,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}